{"tid":389380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個令女友對自己加深感情既行為","createTime":"2017-09-06T08:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T09:25:10.000Z","uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31d1a00d4eb117f57515056c5a7c7565b5acd513","tid":389380,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"要比對方知道 對方係心目中既地位係好重好重<br />\n<br />\n同女友講 有個女仔好似鐘意我<br />\n女友即時反應一定問邊個黎<br />\n但呢個問題無必要答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我最愛既係你 打風都吹唔甩我同你<br />\n我係唔會比第三者介入我同你既感情 <br />\n<br />\n補充:<br />\n其實我同鐘意我既女仔講左 <br />\n死撚開啦 <br />\n我唔想死係我 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">女 朋 友</span></span> 面前 然後個女仔就無再搵過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">初初心大心細 不過將補充既說話講左比女朋友聽<br />\n跟手我就比佢扭住耳仔360度咁轉:</span>) </span>"},{"pid":"cfaa1f78a335079bbdef48a506b8c33a377f2444","tid":389380,"uid":71237,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"提高自己的表達能力"},{"pid":"ac0a90b812a073fcf5c997b186dadc29b8190290","tid":389380,"uid":14474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"你咩事"},{"pid":"f95a10882d791e7dbd1440bbcc675ad056dc3a80","tid":389380,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>提高自己的表達能力</blockquote><br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e02d04e6c0774413581cd17cdfbdd488d378893","tid":389380,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>提高自己的表達能力</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1be16cb335275430e3858eccdaa222b1f6d139f","tid":389380,"uid":50831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re